episodes.title: Judge orders release of Ghislaine Maxwell case files about Jeffrey Epstein
episodes.description:
A judge ordered the release of grand jury transcripts and evidence against Ghislaine Maxwell, an aide to accused sex trafficker Jeffrey Epstein
